The '''Embassy of Palestine in [[Stockholm]]''' ({{lang-ar|السفارة الفلسطينية في ستوكهولم}});  is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[State of Palestine]] in [[Sweden]]. It is the first time a Palestinian embassy has ever opened in a western European nation.<ref>https://www.rt.com/news/231107-palestine-first-embassy-sweden/</ref>

